[`salt.states.file.uncomment`](http://docs.saltstack.com/en/latest/ref/states/all/salt.states.file.html#salt.states.file.uncomment) appears to only support single character comment formats.

Attempting to uncomment a line beginning with `//` with either of these configurations:
- `- char: /`
- `- char: //`

...gives the following error.

> Expected uncommented lines not found
